cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.CC 

This paper deals with the PAC learnability of decision stumps, which is a fundamental concept in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses category theory and measure theory, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also deals with algorithms and data structures, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
